                      The caption may have been added later to an image that is actually depicting the raising of Adam and Eve, who are given halos in this image</desc></decoNote>
                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d5"><locus target="#137r" facs="141"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1066DavidHarp"/> with caption <q>“Saint David.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                      <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d06">
                        Decorative designs:
                        <locus target="#1r"/> (ḥaräg in brown and green ink);
                        <locus target="#7r #14r #21r #30v #37v #42v #50v #60r #67r #72v #83v #93r #96r #101v #107r #118v #124v #125v #127r #128v #130r #131r #132r #133r"
